d data (names, formations, tactics)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Messages sent to AI staff"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Media uploads (photos, videos)"}]]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-medium text-white/80 mt-4 mb-2","children":"Information collected automatically:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"IP address and device information"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Usage analytics (pages visited, features used)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Telegram user ID (when using Telegram Mini App)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Blockchain transaction hashes"}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"2. How We Use Your Information"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Provide and maintain the Platform"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Calculate player attributes, XP, and reputation scores"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Enable peer verification of match results"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Power AI staff insights and tactical recommendations"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Process prediction market bets and treasury transactions"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Send notifications via Telegram or in-app"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improve the Platform through analytics"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Prevent fraud and enforce our terms"}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"3. Data Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-3","children":"We share data with:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Squad members:"}]," Your match stats, ratings, and profile are visible to squad mates"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Blockchain networks:"}]," Match verification data i