ata (profile, match history, AI memory) upon request."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"6. Cookies"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. Analytics cookies (PostHog) are optional and require your consent. See our"," ",["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/cookies","className":"text-green-400 hover:underline","children":"Cookie Policy"}]," ","for details."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"7. Data Retention"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We retain your data while your account is active. Match data and blockchain records are retained indefinitely. AI conversation history is capped at 20 messages per context. Inactive accounts may be archived after 24 months."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"8. Children's Privacy"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"SportWarren is not directed at children under 16. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 16. If you believe a child has provided data, contact us for deletion."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"9. Changes to This Policy"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We may update this policy. Material changes will be communicated via the Platform or email. The \"Last updated\" date at the top reflects the latest revision."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"10. Contact"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Privacy questions or data requests? Contact us at"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"mailto:privacy@sportwarren.com","className":"text-green-400 hover:underline","children":"privacy@sportwarren.com"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex gap-